{"title":"向着闪光的远方","authors":["西中扬"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着闪光的远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西中扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于登上了峭拔的山巅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好不容易甩掉了攀援的艰难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管刺丛中还留着血渍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换来的却是心胸的分外舒展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云海里浮起满怀激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在空谷兴奋地呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳中浮金焕彩的山头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正托起一个个闪光的信念！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登上飞机舷梯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心随时代羽翼腾起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘着万里长风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揽起一天云霓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔日的风风雨雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都向身后飘去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追着飞天神话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向星空云际。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的脚印伸得很远很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着明天不断伸展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象长空中整齐的雁阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向一轮满月的天边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去的荆棘虽未留下血渍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史却把我们推向一个很高的起点。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}